column5: With the warm weather comes so much to do. Spent the morning getting things going in the pepper patch, followed by a wee break at the pond.   Casey has finally decided he likes sushi  Capped the day off with a serious effort in the kitchen. Canning season has officially commenced with the first 2 cases of bread & butter pickles.  Now I can think about bed.
lol. love the photo of Casey and the fish..."what , me ?"
